title: Cave of Eileithyia (Inatos)
description: Sacred cave dedicated to the goddess of childbirth, Eileithyia, at Inatos, Crete. The site was in use from the Geometric period to the Roman period.

properties.description: Point based on an OpenStreetMap node representing the Cave of Eileithyia (Inatos) after Kanta 2022.
